{
  "text": "In the case of a three-level tree, processing colour, motion and depth features, there are six possible permutations of feature order in the tree. Fig. 14 graphs the performance curves of all six permutations, when testing the proposed tracker on five ground-truthed RGB-D sequences drawn from [CITATION_1] benchmark data set. ",
